description: This file defines a React functional component named RestVsMoveBarChart that renders a bar chart using the Recharts library. It visualizes data comparing 'Resting' vs 'Moving' counts with customizable colors and height.

methods.name: RestVsMoveBarChart({ data = [],  height = 280, colors = { Resting: "#1E3A8A", Moving: "#F59E0B" }, })
methods.description: React component that renders a bar chart comparing 'Resting' and 'Moving' data with customizable options.

ctags.name: normalized
ctags.pattern: /^        <BarChart data={normalized} margin={{ top: 8, right: 8, left: 0, bottom: 0 }}>$/

fields.name: <BarChart data={normalized} margin={{ top: 8, right: 8, left: 0, bottom: 0 }}>
